# VibOS Comp Dependency Intelligence

## Purpose

Dependency intelligence prevents stale model memory from choosing old, incompatible, vulnerable, abandoned, or hard-to-upgrade packages.

## Core Question

Are the runtime, package manager, frameworks, packages, versions, lockfiles, and transitive risks backed by current evidence and compatible with each other?

